data.description: Come see this open-concept 4 Bedroom, 3 full bath home located in a swim community just outside of Downtown Braselton! - The welcoming front porch leads to a beautiful entry way w/an abundance of gorgeous crown molding & custom chair rail trim in the entry way & dining room. The spacious kitchen w/a built-in desk features granite counter tops, tile back splash w/ ample counter space, stained brown cabinets, and a large island w/ barstool seating. The extra-wide pantry offers great storage, the built-in hall tree is a convenient drop all when entering from the garage, and the dining area is spacious allowing for ample seating for entertaining. Adjacent to the kitchen is the family room which includes an unobstructed view of the back yard and downstairs living areas. The master BR is enormous & has space to incorporate a sitting area, office, or nursery. The master BA features double vanities, a soaking tub, separate shower, and massive walk-in closet. All secondary BR's are spacious & the Laundry room is conveniently located on the same level as the BR's. The outdoor living space offers many possibilities as the yard is relatively flat and includes a covered back porch.  This home has a great ambience w/ample space making it perfect for entertaining & large family gatherings. This community has a pool, clubhouse, and a private entrance from the neighborhood to a County park. Conveniently located within walking distance to downtown Braselton & Hoschton. Just minutes to I-85. Close to desirable schools, shopping, restaurants, and parks. Come see this great property today!
